rows.label: tlk42350123_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Gula is the best place
for us Phonexes to live.

rows.label: tlk42350123_01_msg0002
rows.name:
There are plenty of trees
and water, lots of food,
and the climate is warm...

rows.label: tlk42350123_01_msg0003
rows.name: That's what my mom and dad said.

rows.label: tlk42350123_01_msg0004
rows.name:
As for me... I kind of think
everywhere is like this, though...
